full_title: Rah Tah Tah by Tyler, The Creator
title: Rah Tah Tah

description.plain:
“Rah Tah Tah” portrays the explosive and chaotic side of CHROMAKOPIA, featuring Tyler, The Creator’s well-known aggressive rap style and production. The song’s premise is laced around Tyler showing off his LaFerrari, as the title imitates the sound of the gas pedal being pressed. Tyler’s LaFerrari, ironically, is referenced often throughout CHROMAKOPIA, most notably in the “Noid” music video and during his third “Sticky” verse.

This track is one of the few songs, teased in the CHROMAKOPIA vinyl promotional video, uploaded to Tyler’s channel on October 22, 2024, where a 12-second part of the song was featured in a medley of different brand new CHROMAKOPIA snippets.
